ty_images/184860418/image_184860418.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">MarsBars</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>It pays to be patient, especially when it comes to income stocks. That\u2019s because being able to layer in at lower prices translates into a higher dividend yield and more income. With the Dow Jones Industrial Index having dropped for 10</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184860418/image_184860418.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745335-american-tower-buy-drop-market-fearful", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 18:00:00"}, {"id": "4745347", "title": "Conagra Brands, Inc. 2025 Q2 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Conagra Brands, Inc. in conjunction with their 2025 Q2 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106250\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745347-conagra-brands-inc-2025-q2-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 17:55:56"}, {"id": "4745330", "title": "Tesla: It's Finally Time To Trim (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508387/image_1288508387.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Tesla Inc offices and production facility in Silicon Valley\" data-id=\"1288508387\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508387/image_1288508387.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508387/image_1288508387.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508387/image_1288508387.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508387/image_1288508387.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508387/image_1288508387.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508387/image_1288508387.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508387/image_1288508387.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508387/image_1288508387.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Sundry Photography/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I've covered <b>Tesla, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TSLA\" title=\"Tesla, Inc.\">TSLA</a></span>) several times in the past. My initial article offered a $412 fair value estimate of the stock and discussed how Tesla is <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4585346-tesla-electrifying-the-earth\">electrifying the earth</a> and</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508387/image_1288508387.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745330-tesla-finally-time-to-trim-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 17:49:12"}, {"id": "4745327", "title": "Drone Wars: Building An All-Drone Stock Portfolio For The Future Of Innovation", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A flying drone\" data-id=\"956306692\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6674px\" height=\"5338px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Yagi Studio</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>What's going on?</h2> <p><span>For those like myself who are <a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/politics/fbi-warns-new-jersey-residents-not-shoot-down-drones-point-lasers-aircraft\" rel=\"nofollow\">keeping abreast</a> of this topic, drones are swarming the New Jersey/NYC area. Many theories of their purpose are floating around, from trying to sniff hazardous materials, to foreign adversaries, hobbyists, or a possible stress</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745327-drone-wars-building-an-all-drone-stock-portfolio-for-the-future-of-innovation", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 17:30:48"}]}